reviewText: Don't' expect 60 minutes here.but  just  1 5 !! I was expecting his one man show on Broadway on this DVD.but all you get is a big bag of nothing..unless you like a brief moment of jackman shaking  his butt from Boy From Oz.
I have watched this dvd at least 25 times so far. I wish it could have been longer but what is on this dvd is wonderful. I love Hugh Jackman and have everything he has ever done.
